cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper focuses on the evaluation of Visual Place Recognition (VPR) techniques, which involves computer vision, robotics, machine learning, artificial intelligence, and multimedia. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of VPR in robotics, which suggests the possibility of it being categorized under cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of state-of-the-art techniques, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) likely categories. Finally, the paper discusses the usage of semantic scene information, which involves multimedia, making cs.MM (Multimedia) a possible category as well.
